reviewText: Another solid product by Tim Tackett.  He does a nice job explaining the various tactics/principles in his JKD approach.
I studied overseas years ago and was glad to get something that was Bruces's. Good service! I would order from this co. again.
This DVD was very insightful in alot of ways. The concepts taught were presented in a manner that is easily understood. My only wish is that I had actual JKD instructors in my area.
